                        <Italic>Explanation of example</Italic> - 1. Minimize IdealAutomate. 2. Launch IE with google as content. 3-6 Click Google Search Button. 7 Use PutCursorPosition to save current cursor position. 8-9 Position cursor on I'm Feeling Lucky Button. 10 Sleep 3 seconds. 11 Position cursor back on google search button.
